  "response": "At Melbourne Airport (Tullamarine), you can find power outlets in several locations:\n\n1. Most terminal waiting areas and departure lounges have power outlets and charging stations\n\n2. Near seating areas in the international and domestic terminals\n\n3. In some caf\u00e9 and restaurant areas where you can sit and charge your device\n\n4. Some gate areas have power outlets integrated into seating\n\n5. Workstations and charging zones in the terminals\n\nTip: If you can't find a convenient outlet, bring a portable power bank as a backup. Also, look for power outlets near walls or close to seating areas.",
